NOTE ON ART ASSETS

The Python source code in this repository is licensed under MIT as above.

The pet SPRITES (PNG files in assets/pets/) are separate copyrightable
works and are NOT automatically covered by the MIT license unless
individually annotated as such. Redistribution or commercial use of
the sprites requires the sprite author's permission. The nine English
Shorthair kittens shipped with this repository were AI-generated and
are provided for personal use with the engine.

Commercial character packs distributed as .perchy-pack files carry
their own license text embedded in the pack (see LICENSE.txt inside
each pack). Buying a pack does not grant redistribution rights unless
that pack's own license explicitly says so.
